    <item>
      <title>如何在使用Hugo模版框架时在文章中嵌入HTML代码</title>
      <link>/posts/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%9C%A8%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8hugo%E6%A8%A1%E7%89%88%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6%E6%97%B6%E5%9C%A8%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E4%B8%AD%E5%B5%8C%E5%85%A5html%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 31 Oct 2023 10:17:52 +0100</pubDate>
      
      <guid>/posts/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%9C%A8%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8hugo%E6%A8%A1%E7%89%88%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6%E6%97%B6%E5%9C%A8%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E4%B8%AD%E5%B5%8C%E5%85%A5html%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81/</guid>
      <description>使用 Hugo 模板框架时，在文章中嵌入 HTML 代码（两种方法）</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2 id="起因">起因</h2>
<p>由于昨天写了一篇关于如何翻墙的文章（我很纠结要不要继续写下去），所以为了自身以后的安全问题，我给它加了一个弹窗来保命（你们怎么选就不关我的事了）.<br>
后来总算是把这个搞成了，但是真的是困难重重啊&hellip;&hellip;</p>
<h2 id="so咋搞的呢">so，咋搞的呢？</h2>
<p>我以前使用的博客系统是Hexo，要是想在markdown文章里加入html代码，那就直接加就行；运行的也嘎嘎流畅.<br>
Hugo就不这样. 因为Hugo的Markdown渲染器会自动忽略Html代码（<code>&lt;br&gt;</code>什么的不算），我认为这个渲染器小心过头了（Html又咋样）.</p>
<p>不过虽然要在文章里嵌入html的人很少（而且Hugo的用户量没有Hexo的多），我也找到了两个方法.</p>
<hr>
<h3 id="方法一------配置文件修改大法">方法一&mdash;&mdash;配置文件修改大法</h3>
<p>在配置文件hugo.yaml里添加几条：</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#f92672">markup</span>:
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>  <span style="color:#f92672">goldmark</span>:
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#f92672">renderer</span>:
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>      <span style="color:#f92672">unsafe</span>: <span style="color:#66d9ef">true</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>我也是吐了：&ldquo;unsafe&quot;是什么鬼？？？自己的博客自己还会添加恶意代码吗？？？<br>
这个方法应该是简单的一个了，还有一个方法，虽然麻烦一点点，但是我也说一下吧.</p>
<h3 id="方法二------shortcode启动">方法二&mdash;&mdash;shortcode，启动！！</h3>
<p>众所周知，Hugo里有一种叫做&quot;shortcode&quot;的玩意（我也不知道是啥，反正这玩意挺有用就对了）. 依靠这玩意的功能，我们也可以在文章中嵌入html代码.</p>
<p>在<code>博客根目录/layouts</code>下新建<code>shortcode</code>文件夹，然后新建<code>raw.html</code>.<br>
打开<code>raw.html</code>，在里面写入下面那行玩意：</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-html" data-lang="html"><span style="display:flex;"><span>{{ .Inner }}
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>这里说一下原理：Hugo的shortcode功能允许你创建shortcode，中文直译就是“短代码”. 这个东西合理配置能发挥很多功能，就像上面的那行.<br>
如果你在文章中要嵌入Html代码，直接把代码复制进去然后用{{&lt;raw&gt;}}和{{&lt;/raw&gt;}}括起来就行.</p>
<p>比如：
<img loading="lazy" src="/images/shortcode.png" alt="代码图片"  />

把上面的玩意嵌入文章，就能用了. 中间的html可以自由发挥.<br>
<em><strong>（你们知道为什么要用图片吗，因为这玩意六亲不认，把它放在markdown代码块、html注释和Hugo短代码注释中居然还能执行html！！！）</strong></em></p>
<p><em><strong>（你们知道我是怎么打出上面的{{&lt;raw&gt;}}和{{&lt;/raw&gt;}}的吗，使用转义代码！！！实际上我这边是这样的：<code>{{&amp;lt;raw&amp;gt;}}和{{&amp;lt;/raw&amp;gt;}}</code>）</strong></em></p>
<h3 id="与此文章相关的还有">与此文章相关的还有：</h3>
<p><a href="/posts/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E7%BB%99hugo%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/">如何给hugo添加评论系统</a><br>
<a href="/posts/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E6%9D%A5%E5%88%B0hugo%E7%9A%84%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AF%87%E5%8D%9A%E6%96%87">第一次来到hugo的第一篇博文</a><br>
<a href="/posts/%E7%BB%99%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E6%94%B9%E5%8A%A8-%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%87%E5%BF%98/">给博客的各种改动-记录以备忘</a></p>
]]></content:encoded>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>给博客的各种改动-记录以备忘</title>
      <link>/posts/%E7%BB%99%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E6%94%B9%E5%8A%A8-%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%87%E5%BF%98/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 29 Oct 2023 09:58:05 +0100</pubDate>
      
      <guid>/posts/%E7%BB%99%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E6%94%B9%E5%8A%A8-%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%87%E5%BF%98/</guid>
      <description>对Hugo博客的美好、添加新功能与魔改</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2 id="对博客的魔改">对博客的魔改</h2>
<h3 id="这篇文章不仅仅是备忘录如果有人认为这些改动不错可以放到自己博客里">这篇文章不仅仅是备忘录，如果有人认为这些改动不错，可以放到自己博客里。</h3>
<h3 id="仅限papermod主题在u这里httpsgithubcomadityatelangehugo-papermodu">仅限PaperMod主题，在<u><a href="https://github.com/adityatelange/hugo-PaperMod"><em><strong>这里</strong></em></a></u></h3>
<h3 id="记录以备忘">记录以备忘</h3>
<hr>
<h3 id="添加版权信息">添加版权信息</h3>
<p>复制<code>主题/layouts/partials/footer.html</code>的文件到<code>博客根目录/layouts/partials/footer.html</code>.注释原来被包裹在了一个<strong>Hugo模板语言</strong>的<code>if语句</code>中的内容.</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-html" data-lang="html"><span style="display:flex;"><span>{{- if not (.Param &#34;hideFooter&#34;) }}
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>&lt;<span style="color:#f92672">footer</span> <span style="color:#a6e22e">class</span><span style="color:#f92672">=</span><span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;footer&#34;</span>&gt;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    {{- if site.Copyright }}
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    &lt;<span style="color:#f92672">span</span>&gt;{{ site.Copyright | markdownify }}&lt;/<span style="color:#f92672">span</span>&gt;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    {{- else }}
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    <span style="color:#75715e">&lt;!--                &lt;-----就是这样注释
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#75715e">    &lt;span&gt;&amp;copy; {{ now.Year }} &lt;a href=&#34;{{ &#34;&#34; | absLangURL }}&#34;&gt;{{ site.Title }}&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#75715e">    --&gt;</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    {{- end }}
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    .......等等
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>&lt;/<span style="color:#f92672">footer</span>&gt;
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>现在跳过if语句，在<code>{{- end }}</code>后面添加了刚刚注释掉的代码，并且添加了2020（本博是2020年搭建的，虽然后来的两年啥也没写，到最后才想起有个博客，如果你们也要添加初始年份把2020改掉就行）.<br>
原代码为：</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-html" data-lang="html"><span style="display:flex;"><span>&lt;<span style="color:#f92672">span</span>&gt;&amp;copy; {{ now.Year }} &lt;<span style="color:#f92672">a</span> <span style="color:#a6e22e">href</span><span style="color:#f92672">=</span><span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;{{ &#34;</span><span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">&#34;</span> <span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">|</span> <span style="color:#a6e22e">absLangURL</span> <span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">}}&#34;</span>&gt;{{ site.Title }}&lt;/<span style="color:#f92672">a</span>&gt;&lt;/<span style="color:#f92672">span</span>&gt;
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>现代码为</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-html" data-lang="html"><span style="display:flex;"><span>&lt;<span style="color:#f92672">span</span>&gt;&amp;copy;2020-{{ now.Year }} 保留所有权利. &lt;<span style="color:#f92672">a</span> <span style="color:#a6e22e">href</span><span style="color:#f92672">=</span><span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;{{ &#34;</span><span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">&#34;</span> <span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">|</span> <span style="color:#a6e22e">absLangURL</span> <span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">}}&#34;</span>&gt;{{ site.Title }}&lt;/<span style="color:#f92672">a</span>&gt;&lt;/<span style="color:#f92672">span</span>&gt;
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>添加了2020、保留所有权利。</p>
<hr>
<h3 id="添加dmca版权保护徽章">添加DMCA版权保护徽章</h3>
<p>还是在此文件中，上面那行代码<strong>之后</strong>添加了DMCA.com中的版权声明，若添加此声明，DMCA.com组织将免费联系盗窃/不合规转载文章的人删除文章。<br>
（此处不展示代码内容，如果你也想添加DMCA的版权保护徽章，可以去它的官网免费获取。<br>
<em><strong><a href="https://www.dmca.com/Badges.aspx">https://www.dmca.com/Badges.aspx</a></strong></em></p>
<hr>
<h3 id="取消由xxxxxx强力驱动的字样">取消由XXX、XXX强力驱动的字样。</h3>
<p>还是在此文件中，查找<code>Powered by</code>，注释了“由Hugo、Papermod强力驱动“字样。</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-html" data-lang="html"><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#75715e">&lt;!--     
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#75715e">    &lt;span&gt;
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#75715e">        Powered by
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#75715e">        &lt;a href=&#34;https://gohugo.io/&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreferrer&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Hugo&lt;/a&gt; &amp;
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#75715e">        &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/adityatelange/hugo-PaperMod/&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;PaperMod&lt;/a&gt;
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#75715e">    &lt;/span&gt;
</span></span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#75715e">     --&gt;</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><hr>
<h3 id="自定义404页面">自定义404页面</h3>
<p>在<code>博客根目录/layouts</code>下新建404.html文件，写入</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-html" data-lang="html"><span style="display:flex;"><span>{{ define &#34;main&#34; }}
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>&lt;<span style="color:#f92672">main</span> <span style="color:#a6e22e">id</span><span style="color:#f92672">=</span><span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;main&#34;</span>&gt;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    &lt;<span style="color:#f92672">div</span>&gt;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        &lt;<span style="color:#f92672">h1</span> <span style="color:#a6e22e">id</span><span style="color:#f92672">=</span><span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;title&#34;</span>&gt;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            &lt;<span style="color:#f92672">p</span> <span style="color:#a6e22e">style</span><span style="color:#f92672">=</span><span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;text-align:center&#34;</span>&gt;404&lt;/<span style="color:#f92672">p</span>&gt;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        &lt;/<span style="color:#f92672">h1</span>&gt;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        &lt;<span style="color:#f92672">br</span>&gt;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        &lt;<span style="color:#f92672">h2</span>&gt;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            &lt;<span style="color:#f92672">p</span> <span style="color:#a6e22e">style</span><span style="color:#f92672">=</span><span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;text-align:center&#34;</span>&gt;You are lost.&lt;/<span style="color:#f92672">p</span>&gt;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        &lt;/<span style="color:#f92672">h2</span>&gt;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        &lt;<span style="color:#f92672">br</span>&gt;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>        &lt;<span style="color:#f92672">h2</span>&gt;&lt;<span style="color:#f92672">a</span> <span style="color:#a6e22e">href</span><span style="color:#f92672">=</span><span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;{{ &#34;</span><span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">&#34;</span> <span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">|</span> <span style="color:#a6e22e">relURL</span> <span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010">}}&#34;</span>&gt;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>                &lt;<span style="color:#f92672">p</span> <span style="color:#a6e22e">style</span><span style="color:#f92672">=</span><span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;text-align:center&#34;</span>&gt;Click To Go Home.&lt;/<span style="color:#f92672">p</span>&gt;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>            &lt;/<span style="color:#f92672">a</span>&gt;&lt;/<span style="color:#f92672">h1</span>&gt;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    &lt;/<span style="color:#f92672">div</span>&gt;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>&lt;/<span style="color:#f92672">main</span>&gt;
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>{{ end }}
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>html文件可以更改为你自己喜欢的404页面，或者去谷歌搜索<code>404页面模板</code>找一个好看的.</p>
<hr>
<h3 id="添加搜索引擎网站验证html元标记">添加搜索引擎网站验证HTML元标记</h3>
<p>打开总配置文件，添加一条<code>analytics.google.SiteVerificationTag: 你的google元标记后面的content里面的内容</code>，注意冒号后面要留空格.</p>
<hr>
<h3 id="添加评论系统">添加评论系统</h3>
<p>此改动见另一篇文章
<em><strong><u><a href="https://charle00001.github.io/posts/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E7%BB%99hugo%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/">点此进入</a></u></strong></em></p>
<hr>
<h3 id="在不破坏hugo模板框架的情况下在页面文章中加入html代码">在不破坏Hugo模板框架的情况下在页面/文章中加入html代码</h3>
<p>请参见这篇文章&mdash;&mdash;<a href="/posts/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%9C%A8%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8hugo%E6%A8%A1%E7%89%88%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6%E6%97%B6%E5%9C%A8%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E4%B8%AD%E5%B5%8C%E5%85%A5html%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81/">在这里</a></p>
<hr>
<h3 id="自定义顶栏">自定义顶栏</h3>
<p>这个很简单，只要在配置文件<code>hugo.yaml/hugo.toml/hugo.json</code>中加上（不要加在params下）：</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#75715e"># 在页面上方加入菜单</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#f92672">menu</span>:
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>  <span style="color:#f92672">main</span>:
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    - <span style="color:#f92672">name</span>: <span style="color:#ae81ff">首页</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>      <span style="color:#f92672">url</span>: <span style="color:#ae81ff">/</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>      <span style="color:#75715e"># 通常根目录为首页</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>      <span style="color:#f92672">weight</span>: <span style="color:#ae81ff">1</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>      <span style="color:#75715e"># weight越小，越靠前</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    - <span style="color:#f92672">name</span>: <span style="color:#ae81ff">标签</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>      <span style="color:#f92672">url</span>: <span style="color:#ae81ff">tags/</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>      <span style="color:#f92672">weight</span>: <span style="color:#ae81ff">2</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    - <span style="color:#f92672">name</span>: <span style="color:#ae81ff">分类</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>      <span style="color:#f92672">url</span>: <span style="color:#ae81ff">categories/</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>      <span style="color:#f92672">weight</span>: <span style="color:#ae81ff">3</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>    - <span style="color:#f92672">name</span>: <span style="color:#ae81ff">XXX</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>      <span style="color:#f92672">url</span>: <span style="color:#ae81ff">XXX</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>      <span style="color:#f92672">weight</span>: <span style="color:#ae81ff">4</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>      <span style="color:#75715e"># XXX什么的自定义，要加别的和这个一样写</span>
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>toml和json可以去寻找yaml to toml/json转换器</p>
<hr>
<h3 id="最后">最后</h3>
<p>如果要自定义一些博客内容，只需要复制<code>主题/layouts/partials</code>里面的html文件（如footer.html）到<code>博客根目录/layouts/partials</code>里面然后更改它的内容就可以了. 这么做不仅可以不破坏主题原本的代码，还能成功自定义.</p>
